high_descs: Walk ahead to the counter, then turn left and walk to the coffee maker.
Take the mug out of the coffee maker.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Wash the mug in the sink.
Turn left and walk back to the coffee maker.
Place the coffee mug back in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean mug in a coffee maker.

anns.task_desc: clean the mug then put it back under the coffee machine

high_descs: Walk forward to the counter then turn left and walk to the coffee maker.
Pick up the dirty mug that's at it's spot under the coffee maker.Turn around and walk to the sink then turn left to face it.
Turn around and walk to the sink on your left then turn left to face it.
Wash the mug in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Go back to the coffee maker.
Put the mug back where you got it from.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean mug under the coffee maker.
